15,01EXPLANATioN oF VARioUS THiNGS
15,01-----------------------------
15,01At the main menu, use the cursor UP and DOWN keys to select a form.
15,01When you have the form you want to fill out highlited, press enter.
15,01F1 will give you basically this.
15,01ALT-A will give you the credits for this program.
15,01To exit, press ALT-X.

15,01If you like this program and you want one done for your group,
